        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Apprenticeship Access for All Act of 2020</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Labor to promote diversity and ensure equal opportunity to participate in programs for apprentices, youth apprentices, and pre-apprentices, including in apprenticeable occupations under the national apprenticeship system. </p>]]></text>
